- üë• **User roles**: finder & owner & drop-pointer
- üêæ **Lost pets page**: dedicated section for reporting and finding lost animals
- üè™ **Drop points**: local shops can register as safe places where found items are stored until the owner retrieves them
- üè† **HomePage**: feed with lost and found items  
- üìç **Map view**: geolocation with pins for drop-point
- üì§ **Upload & share**: add photos and details of found items  
- üõ° **Secure claim**: verification system with unique questions  
- üèÜ **Gamification**: badges and points for active users  

